
.TH "GCLOUD_ALPHA_ML_SPEECH_OPERATIONS_WAIT" 1



.SH "NAME"
.HP
gcloud alpha ml speech operations wait \- poll long\-running speech recognition operation until it completes



.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP
\f5gcloud alpha ml speech operations wait\fR \fIOPERATION\fR [\fIGCLOUD_WIDE_FLAG\ ...\fR]



.SH "DESCRIPTION"

\fB(ALPHA)\fR Poll a long\-running speech recognition operation until it
completes. When the operation is complete, this command will display the results
of the transcription.



.SH "POSITIONAL ARGUMENTS"

.RS 2m
.TP 2m
\fIOPERATION\fR
The ID of the operation to wait for.


.RE
.sp

